## ⚙️ Compilation & Execution Diagnostics

To prevent aggressive compiler optimization from hiding undefined behavior, run this repository with strict sanitizers enabled.

```bash
# 1. Compile with AddressSanitizer and strict warnings
gcc -Wall -Wextra -Werror -fsanitize=address -g src/0x02_MEMORY_SAFETY.c -o mem_test

# 2. Check for memory leaks via Valgrind (if ASan is disabled)
valgrind --leak-check=full --track-origins=yes ./mem_test
```

